    Page: 40
    Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Cause
---
Nothing in all Nature is more certain than the fact that no single thing or
event can stand alone. It is attached to all that has gone before it, and
it will remain attached to all that will follow it. It was born of some
cause, and so it must be followed by some effect in an endless chain.
